      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_54gc' title='Col. 54GC &mdash; HL Deb 15 June 2000 vol 613 c54GC' name='column_54gc' href='#column_54gc' rel='bookmark'>54GC</a>
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0613P0-05745'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0613P0_20000615_GCR_194' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        <span class="member">Lord McIntosh of Haringey</span> moved Amendment No. 73:
