      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0613P0-05747'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0613P0_20000615_GCR_196' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        <span class="member">Lord McIntosh of Haringey</span> moved Amendment No. 74:
